REVISION INSTRUCTIONS FOR THE EXISTING INDIVA FIGMA DESIGN SYSTEM:

The current concept should NO LONGER behave like a single scrolling landing page. Redesign the product architecture into a realistic multi-page premium social impact platform with proper navigation, page hierarchy, mobile responsiveness, and production-grade UX patterns.

The overall aesthetic, color palette, typography, and emotional storytelling direction should remain the same:

* Apple-inspired minimalism
* Airbnb warmth
* Editorial storytelling
* Calm premium nonprofit experience

KEEP:

* Manrope typography
* Indigo palette (#71648C primary)
* Powdered Sugar backgrounds
* Rounded rectangular buttons
* Soft shadows
* Premium whitespace
* Emotional storytelling
* Connected Embrace logo direction

NEW PRODUCT ARCHITECTURE:

The platform should feel like:

* a real funded startup
* production-ready
* thoughtfully structured
* emotionally immersive

NOT:

* a giant one-page portfolio
* a Dribbble-style scrolling concept
* an animation showcase

